										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>7 of the Most Inventive Cart Abandonment Popup Examples We’ve Seen</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/list-building" rel="category tag">List Building</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Cart Abandonment Popup Examples [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-76398" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Cart-Abandonment-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e789f0d7e4f0" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re in e-commerce, you’re probably trying different strategies to reduce cart abandonment.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Maybe you haven’t reached the results you’re aiming for or you want to achieve even lower cart abandonment rates.<br></p>



<p>You know the importance of well-written <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/abandoned-cart-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">abandoned cart emails</a> and how they can boost your conversion rates.<br></p>



<p>But are you making the most of your on-site messages to stop abandoning visitors?<br></p>



<p>With timely cart abandonment popups, you can convince more visitors to stay on your site, collect warm leads, gather valuable insights, and increase your sales.<br></p>



<p>The best part is, you don’t have to discount your products or offer free shipping to every visitor in order to achieve these goals.<br></p>



<p>In this article, you’ll read seven little-known strategies to convert abandoning visitors into customers. Plus, I’ll show you my favorite cart abandonment popup examples from top e-commerce brands.<br></p>


