<h2 id="Nudge-(Some)-Visitors-with-Free-Shipping"><strong>1. Nudge (Some) Visitors with Free Shipping</strong></h2>



<p>Visitors might leave your site without completing their order for several reasons:&nbsp;<br></p>



<ul><li>An underoptimized <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">checkout</a> process;&nbsp;</li><li>The lack of a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/satisfaction-guarantees" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">satisfaction guarantee</a>;&nbsp;</li><li>A simple distraction you can’t foresee;</li><li>The list goes on</li></ul>



<p>But the number one reason for cart abandonment, <a href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">according to Baymard</a>, is unexpected extra costs, such as shipping.<br></p>



<p>Offering free shipping on your site doesn’t only increase conversions, but it also urges visitors to spend more.<br></p>



<p>In fact, <a href="https://www.invespcro.com/blog/free-shipping/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">93% of consumers</a> tend to buy more products if the online store offers free shipping.<br></p>



<p>If you already offer free shipping, you might be thinking that it’s enough to write it down on your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product pages</a>.<br></p>



<p>But free shipping is only an incentive if you nudge visitors with it when they’re about to leave their cart.<br></p>



<p>So if you’re offering free shipping, make sure you always remind your visitors about it with a timely popup.<br></p>



<p>Here’s the popup <a href="https://www.katespade.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Kate Spade</a> displays when you’re about to leave your basket:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="598" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-1024x598.png" alt="Kate Spade Free Shipping Popup" class="wp-image-76410" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-1024x598.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-300x175.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-768x448.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-380x222.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-600x350.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-760x444.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-740x432.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-220x128.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup-385x225.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Kate-Spade-Free-Shipping-Popup.png 1120w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>With the title “Congratulations!,” the company gets your attention and informs you that you qualify for both free shipping and free returns.<br></p>



<p>Even though they include in the checkout details that you don’t have to pay for shipping, Kate Spade makes sure that you are aware of it before you leave your items behind.<br></p>



<p>Given that not all e-commerce brands are as big as Kate Spade, you might consider offering free shipping only for expensive purchases.<br></p>



<p>If you’re a Sleeknote user and add the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/sitedata" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">SiteData condition</a> to your campaigns, you can detect a customer’s basket value and trigger a free shipping popup for visitors with over a certain amount of basket value.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how such a campaign might look like:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="591" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-1024x591.jpg" alt="Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2" class="wp-image-76430" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-1024x591.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-300x173.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-768x444.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-380x219.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-600x347.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-760x439.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-61x35.jpg 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-87x50.jpg 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-740x427.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-220x127.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2-385x222.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Sleeknote-SiteData-Use-Case-2.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Change your campaign’s condition to <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/exit-intent" target="_blank">exit-intent</a> and you can convert abandoners with a tempting offer before they leave.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
