										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>7 of the Most Creative Sales Promotion Popup Examples We’ve Seen</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/list-building" rel="category tag">List Building</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-87492" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Social-Proof-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e8b264d72f82" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There’s a common misconception among many marketers: </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">“Popups are only for collecting email addresses.”</span></i></p>
</div>






<p>That’s true—but only if you fail to use <a href="https://sleeknote.com/email-popup" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email popups</a> to their full potential.<br></p>



<p>If you want to promote your products and inform website visitors about your current offers, popups are the perfect tool to achieve that.<br></p>



<p>When I say popups, though, I’m not talking about intrusive, full-screen messages. You know, the ones that appear the minute you land on a website and cause you to reach for the close button immediately.<br></p>



<p>Instead, I’m talking about <strong>relevant, timely, </strong>and <strong>non-intrusive </strong>sales promotion popups that inform, rather than irritate, website visitors when browsing online.<br></p>



<p>They’re super effective at <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-sales-funnel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">nudging prospects down your funnel</a>. So, today, I’ll share how to create sales promotion popups the right way, using seven examples we’ve seen from top online brands.<br></p>


