<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Discounts and Coupons</strong></h2>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Discounts</a> are, doubtlessly, one of the most powerful weapons in an e-commerce marketer’s arsenal.<br></p>



<p>When used sparingly, discounts act as a powerful incentive that convert website visitors into subscribers and customers.<br></p>



<p>While there’s more than one way to use discounts and coupons in your popups, here are three of my favorite strategies.<br></p>





<h3><strong>i. Collect Email Addresses</strong></h3>



<p>You can’t convert all website visitors into customers at once. That’s a given. But what you can do, instead, is capture their email addresses and nurture them with <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">the right emails</a> (that is, until they’re ready to take the next step in their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">customer journey</a>.)<br></p>



<p>While doing that, you need to give prospects a valid reason to sign up for your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">email list</a>, be it the content of your weekly newsletter or early access to your sales before anyone else.<br></p>



<p>Unsurprisingly, offering discount codes upon signup, as <a href="https://sleeknote.com/success-stories/apuls" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Apuls</a> does, also helps you grow your email list.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="911" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-1024x911.jpg" alt="Apuls Collect Email Addresses Campaign" class="wp-image-87412" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-1024x911.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-300x267.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-768x683.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-380x338.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-600x534.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-760x676.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-39x35.jpg 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-56x50.jpg 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-551x490.jpg 551w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-220x196.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign-385x342.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Collect-Email-Addresses-Campaign.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Apuls incentivizes new signups with a special discount.</em></p>





<p>In this popup, Apuls offers 200 Danish kroner off your purchase when you sign up for its newsletter. Notice how the company segments its new leads by asking gender information so they can target its subscribers with relevant email campaigns later.<br></p>



<p>To remove any possible friction, Apuls immediately shows your discount code in the success step of this campaign:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="679" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-1024x679.jpg" alt="Apuls Campaign Success Step" class="wp-image-87408" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-1024x679.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-300x200.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-768x509.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-380x252.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-600x398.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-760x504.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-53x35.jpg 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-75x50.jpg 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-740x490.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-220x146.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step-385x255.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apuls-Campaign-Success-Step.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This way, visitors can quickly start browsing and use their discount code, without leaving the page to check their inboxes. And even if they don’t buy anything at this time, Apuls can retarget them in the future with different incentives.<br></p>



<p>This campaign, which converted at <strong>5.13 percent,</strong> helped Apuls combat <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/abandoned-cart-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">cart abandonment</a> effectively and collect quality leads. It’s a simple yet effective tactic you can replicate for your online store.<br></p>





<h3><strong>ii. Increase Product Sales</strong></h3>



<p>While discounts are effective in capturing top-funnel leads, they also help convert prospects who are further down your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-sales-funnel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">sales funnel</a>.<br></p>



<p>With timely <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/sales-promotion-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">sales promotion</a> popups, you can convince on-the-fence prospects to buy from you and increase the ROI of your sales campaigns.<br></p>



<p>Check out this simple promotion popup <a href="https://sleeknote.com/success-stories/sofacompany" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Sofacompany</a> uses on their homepage:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-1024x575.png" alt="Sofacompany Sales Promotion Campaign" class="wp-image-87496" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-768x431.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-1536x863.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-380x213.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-1440x809.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sofacompany-Sales-Promotion-Campaign-385x216.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This popup successfully delivers the message without hurting the user experience. It also blends seamlessly with the website design while still standing out to catch the visitors’ attention.<br></p>



<p>If you want to make your popups easier to engage with, add a benefit-driven <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">call-to-action</a> (CTA) that takes users to your sales pages.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
