</div></div>





<h3><strong>iii. Combine the Two</strong></h3>



<p>Most sales promotion popups, typically, focus on one of the goals above. Companies like <a href="https://www.byravn.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">byRavn</a>, however, cleverly combine the two.<br></p>



<p>Aiming to capitalize on the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-email-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">holiday shopping season</a>, byRavn targets visitors who are on the hunt for gifts. But the company does that subtly. First, by showing a teaser before triggering the popup:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="590" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-1024x590.png" alt="byRavn Teaser" class="wp-image-87436" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-1024x590.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-300x173.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-768x443.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-380x219.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-600x346.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-760x438.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-61x35.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-87x50.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-740x427.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-220x127.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser-385x222.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Teaser.png 1211w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Notice how byRavn adds a product image and the discount code to the teaser, so you can easily see the code and continue shopping without getting disturbed.<br></p>



<p>But if you want to find out more, you can click the teaser inviting you to save 15% off selected products and view this popup:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="931" height="682" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign.png" alt="byRavn Newsletter Campaign" class="wp-image-87432" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign.png 931w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-300x220.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-768x563.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-380x278.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-600x440.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-760x557.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-669x490.png 669w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/byRavn-Newsletter-Campaign-385x282.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 931px) 100vw, 931px" /></figure></div>



<p>byRavn then builds its sales promotion popup with a smart twist. Instead of gating its offer, the company gives you the discount code and encourages you to sign up for its email list <strong>if you want to hear about similar offers in the future.</strong><br></p>



<p>This is a brilliant way to use popups for both promoting your sales campaigns and to collect interested leads by highlighting your newsletter benefit.<br></p>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Limited-Time Offers</strong></h2>



<p>Much like <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">scarcity</a> and urgency, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">limited-time offers</a> have a proven track record in converting visitors into customers.<br></p>



<p>If you’re running a limited-time campaign, however, you need to ensure that as many visitors as possible are aware of it before the time runs out. The most effective way to create that sense of urgency without disturbing your visitors is with well-timed popups.<br></p>



<p>While most marketers associate limited-time offers with flash sales, there’s certainly more to it.<br></p>



<p>Let’s see three examples of how you can use sales promotion popups to support your limited-time offers.<br></p>





<h3><strong>i. Limited-Time Discounts</strong></h3>



<p>If you’re running a sales campaign or offering a discount code only valid for a specific time, you need to communicate the time restrictions clearly.<br></p>



<p>To achieve that, you can add a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/countdown-timer" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">countdown timer</a> to your popups to improve the effectiveness of your limited-time discounts with a sense of urgency.<br></p>



<p>While doing that, you need to remember to highlight in your popup copy:<br></p>



<ul><li>The benefit of making a purchase (i.e., the value of saving;) and</li><li>How visitors can redeem their discount code.</li></ul>



<p>Here’s how your popup might look:</p>


<div id="campaign-template-block_5f71d9fcdc570" class="block-campaign-template">
    <div class="template-placeholder">
    <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Limited-Time-Discount-Popup.png" title="Create a similar campaign">        <p class="image-caption">Create a similar campaign</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="tag">NEW</div>
        <div class="cta-block-content">
            <p>Like what you see? Load this high-converting template in our editor and customize it to the look and feel of your business.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="https://sleeknote.com/template-signup/?templateId=Subscriber-OnlyDiscount&#038;goalId=promote">Try it out</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<div id="editors-note-block_5f71da1edc571" class="block-editors-note">
