<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>
</div>
    <div class="author">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Sam-120x120.png" width="120" height="120" alt="Sam Thomas Davies" class="avatar avatar-120 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-120 alignnone photo" /><div class="author-data"><div class="name">Sam Thomas Davies</div><div class="title">Head of Content</div></div>    </div>
</div>






<p>Make sure your CTA button reminds users of the benefit of taking action, and it sends shoppers in the right direction.<br></p>





<h3><strong>ii. Limited-Time Free Shipping</strong></h3>



<p>If you think that discounting your products will lower their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/perceived-value" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">perceived value</a>, or if you simply can’t afford to reduce your prices—you’re not alone.<br></p>



<p>The good news is, by offering free shipping as an incentive, you can remove a significant obstacle to buying and convert more visitors into customers.<br></p>



<p>Best of all, you don’t have to offer free shipping all year round for it to be effective. With a limited-time free shipping campaign, you can encourage visitors to buy from you, and boost your sales.<br></p>



<p>Similar to any limited-time campaign, a compelling popup, such as <a href="https://www.hairoutlet.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">HairOutlet</a>’s, can help improve your conversions:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="608" height="341" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Hair-Outlet-Free-Shipping-Popup.gif" alt="Hair Outlet Free Shipping Popup" class="wp-image-87448"/></figure></div>



<p>By using a countdown timer, an eye-catching image, and triggering <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/fomo-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">fear-of-missing-out</a> (FOMO), the company gives us a perfect example of promoting limited-time free shipping offers.<br></p>





<h3><strong>iii. Limited-Time Freebies</strong></h3>



<p>Discount codes and free shipping are, doubtlessly, high-converting incentives. Yet, it’s almost impossible to resist the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/power-words" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">power word</a> “free.”<br></p>



<p>Granted, giving your products away isn’t a sustainable long-term strategy, but it works like a charm as a limited-time incentive.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at <a href="https://www.barkbox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">BarkBox’s</a> popup promoting a limited-time freebie:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="528" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-1024x528.png" alt="BarkBox Limited-Time Freebies" class="wp-image-87416" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-1024x528.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-300x155.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-768x396.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-380x196.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-600x309.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-760x392.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-97x50.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-740x381.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-220x113.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies-385x198.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Limited-Time-Freebies.png 1321w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In this simple popup, BarkBox offers new customers two additional products in their subscription box. By using the pre-title “ends today,” the company makes it clear that this is a limited-time offer.<br></p>



<p>While the above popup might work just fine, I tweaked BarkBox’s campaign slightly to include a countdown timer:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="883" height="736" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example.png" alt="BarkBox Popup Example" class="wp-image-87420" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example.png 883w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-300x250.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-768x640.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-380x317.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-600x500.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-760x633.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-588x490.png 588w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-220x183.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/BarkBox-Popup-Example-385x321.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 883px) 100vw, 883px" /></figure></div>



<p>In this version, a ticking countdown timer makes the time constraint clearer and nudges visitors to place an order before the time runs out. It’s a small addition that can do wonders for your conversion rates.<br></p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Giveaway Popups</strong></h2>



<p>Whether you’re aiming to grow your email list, promote a new brand collaboration, or increase your sales, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/giveaway-ideas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">giveaways</a> are one of the most effective tools you can use.<br></p>



<p>Hosting a contest on your site gives you full control over, both in terms of how you manage and promote your giveaway. With eye-catching popups, you can inform visitors about your giveaway at the right time and invite them to join.<br></p>



<p>Here are two examples of how to do that, depending on your conversion goals.<br></p>





<h3><strong>i. Collect Email Addresses</strong></h3>



<p>A compelling giveaway with a relevant prize acts as a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/evergreen-lead-magnet" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">lead magnet</a>, helping you grow your email list with interested prospects.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.jyskvin.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Jysk Vin</a> is aware of this. That’s why the company regularly draws winners out of its email list to encourage new signups. When you enter their website, first, they show you a teaser that reads “Win 36 Bottles”:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="583" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-1024x583.png" alt="JyskVin Giveaway Teaser" class="wp-image-87456" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-1024x583.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-300x171.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-768x437.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-380x216.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-600x341.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-760x432.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-88x50.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-740x421.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-220x125.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser-385x219.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Teaser.png 1225w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you’re visiting an online wine store, it’s safe to assume that you’re open to winning 36 bottles. With this benefit-driven CTA, Jysk Vin makes it easy for visitors to click the teaser and see this campaign:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="606" height="855" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup.png" alt="JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup" class="wp-image-87460" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup.png 606w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup-213x300.png 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup-380x536.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup-600x847.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup-347x490.png 347w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup-220x310.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/JyskVin-Giveaway-Popup-385x543.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 606px) 100vw, 606px" /></figure></div>



<p>In it, Jysk Vin asks once again if you want to win 36 bottles of wine (valued over 3,400 KR.) And if your answer is “yes,” they invite you to join their newsletter.<br></p>



<p>More importantly, rather than simply write “Sign Up” or “Join Giveaway,” Jysk Vin cleverly crafts a CTA button that reads “Enter and Win.”<br></p>



<p>It’s a smart giveaway popup you can use on your site to convert new visitors into subscribers.<br></p>





<h3><strong>ii. Reduce Cart Abandonment</strong></h3>



<p>Contrary to popular belief, giveaways can help you achieve more than just collecting emails.<br></p>



<p>With a timely popup that shows during <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">checkout</a>, you can encourage visitors to place an order to enter your giveaway and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">reduce cart abandonment</a>.<br></p>



<p>Here’s what your campaign might look like:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="564" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-1024x564.png" alt="Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example" class="wp-image-87480" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-1024x564.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-300x165.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-768x423.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-1536x847.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-380x209.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-600x331.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-760x419.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-1440x794.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-91x50.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-740x408.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-220x121.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example-385x212.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Skincare-Giveaway-Popup-Example.png 1593w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you want to show this popup <strong>only</strong> to customers with a certain basket value, you can use our <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/sitedata" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">SiteData condition</a> to convert high-value orders.<br></p>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Seasonal Campaigns</strong></h2>



<p>Halloween, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Black Friday</a>, Christmas, and others… There’s always a holiday around the corner that you can use as an excuse to promote your products.<br></p>



<p>During this busy shopping season, you need eye-catching promotional popups if you want to capitalize on your holiday traffic.<br></p>



<p>Check out this Black Friday popup <a href="https://www.woolandthegang.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Wool and the Gang</a> uses to promote their offers:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-1024x510.png" alt="Wool and the Gang Black Friday Popup" class="wp-image-87516" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-768x383.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-1536x765.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-2048x1020.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-760x379.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-740x369.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-220x110.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Wool-and-the-Gang-Black-Friday-Popup-385x192.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This popup stands out in the website design, yet, doesn’t hurt the browsing experience. If you want to take this campaign to the next level, you can add <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/product-recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">dynamic product recommendations</a> to it:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="716" height="862" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example.png" alt="Black Friday Popup Example" class="wp-image-87424" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example.png 716w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example-249x300.png 249w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example-380x457.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example-600x722.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example-29x35.png 29w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example-42x50.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example-407x490.png 407w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example-220x265.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-Example-385x464.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 716px) 100vw, 716px" /></figure></div>



<p>This way, you can give visitors a place to start browsing and use their discount code.<br></p>



<p>One of my all-time favorite <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/seasonal-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">seasonal marketing strategies</a> is creating an advent calendar that allows visitors to open a new door (to unlock a new offer) every day until Christmas.<br></p>



<p>With an on-site Christmas calendar, you can engage your visitors for a whole month and keep them coming back to your site every day.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at this popup example by <a href="https://www.takeoffer.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Take Offer</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="468" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-1024x468.png" alt="Take Offer Christmas Calendar" class="wp-image-87508" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-1024x468.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-300x137.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-768x351.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-600x274.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-760x347.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-77x35.png 77w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-740x338.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-385x176.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar.png 1344w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>With it, the company invites you to open a new door in their Christmas calendar and when you click the CTA button, Take Offer sends you to this dedicated <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-landing-page" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">landing page</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="928" height="745" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page.png" alt="Take Offer Christmas Calendar Landing Page" class="wp-image-87504" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page.png 928w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-300x241.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-768x617.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-380x305.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-600x482.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-760x610.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-44x35.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-62x50.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-610x490.png 610w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-220x177.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-385x309.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 928px) 100vw, 928px" /></figure></div>



<p>On this page, Take Offer compiles their daily offers, where you can click today’s date to enter that day’s giveaway. Naturally, you’re asked to sign up for the company’s email list to do that:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="934" height="553" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2.png" alt="Take Offer Christmas Calendar Landing Page 2" class="wp-image-87500" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2.png 934w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-300x178.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-768x455.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-380x225.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-600x355.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-760x450.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-59x35.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-740x438.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-220x130.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Take-Offer-Christmas-Calendar-Landing-Page-2-385x228.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 934px) 100vw, 934px" /></figure></div>



<p>This strategy takes time and effort, that’s a given. But it’s a smart way to engage website visitors during a busy <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-gift-guides" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">gift-shopping</a> month and potentially increase your sales.<br></p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Exclusive Offers</strong></h2>



<p>No two website visitors are alike. One user might land on your homepage for the very first time, whereas another might be a frequent buyer.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>By showing different popups to different users based on where they are in the buyer’s journey, you can align your messages with their needs and wishes.<br></p>



<p>Whether you want to target and reward a newsletter subscriber or a repeat customer with promotional popups, the key is to create a sense of <em>exclusivity.</em><br></p>



<p>Check out this subscriber-only popup example:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="926" height="836" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VIP-Sale-Popup-Example-1.gif" alt="VIP-Sale-Popup-Example-1" class="wp-image-87512"/></figure></div>



<p>If you’re planning a sales campaign, consider rewarding your subscribers with early access, or a simple “heads up” about the upcoming sales. It helps create anticipation, encourages users to discover products they might want to buy in advance, and improves your relationship with your subscribers.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Sleeknote Insider Tip</strong></h3>



<p>To make sure your campaign shows only to existing subscribers, use our Newsletter Subscriber condition.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="776" height="662" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Newsletter-Subscriber-Condition-2.gif" alt="Newsletter Subscriber Condition" class="wp-image-87476"/></figure></div>
</div></div>





<p>If you want to go the extra mile for your customers, you can create a special sales campaign for your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">loyalty club</a> members and promote it with a popup like this:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="701" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-1024x701.png" alt="Members-Only-Campaign" class="wp-image-87468" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-1024x701.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-300x205.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-768x526.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-380x260.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-600x411.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-760x520.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-716x490.png 716w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-220x151.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign-385x263.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Members-Only-Campaign.png 1147w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Ideal for engaging return visitors and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-retention-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">retaining</a> your customer base.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Sleeknote Insider Tip</strong></h3>



<p>With our SiteData condition, you can set this campaign to show only<strong> </strong>to logged-in members.<br></p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Cross-Sell Campaigns</strong></h2>



<p>It’s no secret that cross-selling is the perfect tool to increase customers’ <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/average-order-value" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">average order value</a> (AOV).&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>However, cross-selling only works as intended if you do it at the <em>right place</em> and at the <em>right time</em>. Otherwise, you’ll end up with annoyed visitors who’ll never return to your site, and likely move on to a competitor.<br></p>



<p>The key to successful cross-sell campaigns is to show the right <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendation-popups" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product recommendation popups</a> to the right users—when they need them.<br></p>



<p>Take a look at this example:<br></p>


<div id="campaign-template-block_5f71dd06dc572" class="block-campaign-template">
    <div class="template-placeholder">
    <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Cross-Sell-Popup.png" title="Create a similar campaign">        <p class="image-caption">Create a similar campaign</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="tag">NEW</div>
        <div class="cta-block-content">
            <p>Like what you see? Load this high-converting template in our editor and customize it to the look and feel of your business.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="https://sleeknote.com/template-signup/?templateId=RecommendedAccessories&#038;goalId=promote">Try it out</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<p>With a promotional popup that shows on your <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-examples" target="_blank">product pages</a>, you can recommend similar or complimentary items and increase your AOV. (Just remember to give visitors some time to look around before showing your campaign.)<br></p>



<p>If you want to nudge customers to spend more when they’re closer to placing their order, you can show a popup during checkout that invites them to buy more products.<br></p>



<p>For this popup to convert well, however, you need to fulfill at least two criteria:<br></p>



<ol><li>Recommend relevant products; and</li><li>Offer a compelling incentive.</li></ol>



<p>Just like this:</p>


<div id="campaign-template-block_5f71dd31dc573" class="block-campaign-template">
    <div class="template-placeholder">
    <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/CrossSellingonLowOrders.png" title="Create a similar campaign">        <p class="image-caption">Create a similar campaign</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="tag">NEW</div>
        <div class="cta-block-content">
            <p>Like what you see? Load this high-converting template in our editor and customize it to the look and feel of your business.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="https://sleeknote.com/template-signup/?templateId=CrossSellingonLowOrders&#038;goalId=promote">Try it out</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<p>Whether it’s free shipping, a free sample, or a free product, adding a compelling incentive to your popup encourages customers to spend more, without hurting the user experience.<br></p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Surprise Deals</strong></h2>



<p>Although most sales promotion popups can’t go beyond being a simple “10% off” announcement, yours don’t have to be the same. After all, who says you can’t have a little fun with your popups?<br></p>



<p>By adding the element of surprise to your campaigns, you can make your deals more interesting and memorable.<br></p>



<p>While the only limit to how you can use mystery in your campaigns is your imagination, I’ll show you three of my favorites.<br></p>



<p>Surprise deals are a year-round sales promotion tactic, but they’re <em>most</em> effective when they’re <em>least </em>expected. Around a time like Black Friday or Valentine’s Day, when every online store kills the element of surprise with fifty-percent-off banners, you can make your popups click-worthy by hiding your offers:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="926" height="835" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup.png" alt="Black-Friday-Popup" class="wp-image-87428" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup.png 926w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-300x271.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-768x693.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-380x343.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-600x541.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-760x685.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-55x50.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-543x490.png 543w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-220x198.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Black-Friday-Popup-385x347.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 926px) 100vw, 926px" /></figure></div>



<p>Another way you can add mystery to your popups is by building anticipation for your upcoming sales campaign or product launch:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="745" height="803" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup.png" alt="Mystery Deal Popup" class="wp-image-87472" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup.png 745w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup-278x300.png 278w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup-380x410.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup-600x647.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup-32x35.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup-46x50.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup-455x490.png 455w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup-220x237.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mystery-Deal-Popup-385x415.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /></figure></div>



<p>This is the perfect chance to tease your new product line or your next big sales campaign by combining mystery with FOMO.<br></p>



<p>My all-time favorite mystery tactic comes from <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Harry’s</a>. When you add a product to your cart and proceed to checkout, Harry’s show you this popup asking you to add some mystery to your box:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="477" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-1024x477.png" alt="Harry_s-Upsell-Popup" class="wp-image-87452" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-1024x477.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-768x358.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-600x279.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-760x354.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-740x345.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-385x179.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Upsell-Popup.png 1387w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>By paying only £5, you can add even more excitement to your unboxing experience. And if you’re a more rational buyer, Harry’s appeals to you too by saying your mystery product will be <em>worth more than £5.</em><br></p>



<p>This is a brilliant tactic to increase AOV with a mysterious product recommendation popup that you can easily replicate for your business.<br></p>


