										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center">7 Fashion Popup Examples You’ll Want to Copy in 2021</h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/list-building" rel="category tag">List Building</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Fashion Popup Examples [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-96780" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fashion-Popup-Examples-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5ecf87a62c6b6" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">By the year 2022, fashion e-commerce revenue is expected to reach </span><a href="https://www.shopify.com/plus/industry-reports/fashion-and-apparel" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">$713 billion</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> worldwide. With this pace of growth and the ever-increasing competition, more and more apparel retailers are focusing on growing their online traffic.</span></p>
</div>






<p>While doing that, however, many <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/apparel-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">apparel marketers</a> forget that it’s not a matter of bringing visitors to your store anymore. Rather, it’s about <em>how you treat </em>those visitors.</p>



<p>If you’re showing a single, generic popup to every visitor on all your pages, you’ll likely convert a tiny portion of them—at the cost of annoying a bigger percentage.</p>



<p>What I suggest (and what exceptional fashion e-tailers are doing) is using multiple popups, each serving different goals at different times. This way, you can nudge each visitor to take action depending on <em>where they are</em> in the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">buyer’s journey</a>.</p>



<p>To help with that, I’ve gathered seven high-converting fashion popup examples that every apparel store should use (plus how you can easily set them up).</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f406d8dc96" class="block-content-upgrade">
