<p><a href="#7">7. Floyd’s Shopping Assistance Popup</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Ny Form’s Giveaway Popup</strong></h2>



<p>Fashion or not, on-site giveaways are a foolproof way to quickly <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">grow an email list</a> for any e-tailer.</p>



<p>Although giveaways are effective in <a href="https://sleeknote.com/collect-email-addresses" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">collecting email addresses</a>, the quality of your new signups, however, depends heavily on your giveaway’s prize.</p>



<p>Choose an irrelevant (albeit expensive) prize and you’ll only attract spammers. Put your own products on display, however, and you’ll collect relevant leads who are interested in your products, whether or not they win the competition.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.ny-form.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Ny Form</a>, a Danish sports clothing company, is aware of this. That’s why they’re using one of their products as a prize and running a giveaway directly through their website popups.</p>



<p>But unlike many others, Ny Form invites you to join their giveaway gently, first, with a teaser:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="385" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Ny-Form-Teaser.gif" alt="Ny Form Teaser" class="wp-image-96848"/></figure></div>



<p>In this eye-catching teaser (that acts as a preview of the popup), the company cleverly uses a GIF to reveal the prize. And the teaser copy reads, “Win a Backpack from 2117 of Sweden.”</p>



<p>When you click the teaser (or stay on the page for a few seconds,) this <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/slide-in-popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">slide-in</a> appears:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="700" height="414" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Ny-Form-Popup.gif" alt="Ny Form Popup" class="wp-image-96844"/></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Win a backpack from 2117 of Sweden in your preferred color. Just sign up for our newsletter. We’ll find a winner in 4 days, 8 hours, 1 minute.</em></p>





<p>Once again, Ny Form uses a GIF with rotating images of what you can win. It’s smart because when you read the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/popup-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">popup copy</a>, you learn that you can win a backpack in your preferred color (which all the visual cues point to).</p>



<p>Ny Form’s giveaway popup works well for at least a few reasons:</p>



<ul><li>Benefit-driven teaser copy and a compelling headline: “Win a Stylish Backpack”;</li><li>A well-positioned prize;</li><li>Clear and straightforward instructions: “Just sign up for our newsletter”; and</li><li>An evocative <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">call-to-action</a> (CTA) that evokes a feeling of success: “Sign Up and Win.”</li></ul>



<p>Ny Form also uses a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/countdown-timer" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">countdown timer</a> in its popup to communicate when the giveaway will end. This drives a sense of urgency, which nudges their visitors to sign up before the time runs out.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Further Reading</strong></h3>





<ul><li><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/giveaway-ideas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">7 Creative (On-Site) Giveaway Ideas You Can Try Today</a></li></ul>
</div></div>





<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Sleeknote Insider Tip</h3>



<p>Following Ny Form’s recipe, you can easily create a giveaway popup that’ll grow your email list. The star of this popup is, undoubtedly, countdown timer. With Sleeknote, adding a countdown timer to your popups is as easy as a dragging-and-dropping an element.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img width="650" height="361" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Countdown-Timer.gif" alt="Countdown Timer" class="wp-image-96764"/></figure></div>
</div></div>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Kaufmann’s Customer Club Popup</strong></h2>



<p>There are countless ways to collect emails on your fashion site: offering discount codes, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-lead-magnets">lead magnets</a>, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/lead-generation-quizzes" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">quizzes</a>, giveaways, and more.</p>



<p>While a one-time giveaway gives your email list an immediate boost, men’s fashion store <a href="https://www.kaufmann.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Kaufmann</a> uses a more sustainable strategy.</p>



<p>When you visit the website, Kaufmann, first, shows you a teaser that reads “Win a 1,000 kr. Gift Card”:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="549" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-1024x549.png" alt="Kaufmann Teaser" class="wp-image-96812" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-1024x549.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-300x161.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-768x412.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-1536x824.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-2048x1099.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-380x204.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-600x322.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-760x408.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-1440x773.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-65x35.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-93x50.png 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-740x397.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-220x118.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Teaser-385x207.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Win a 1,000 Kr. Gift Card</em></p>





<p>At first, it looks like any other giveaway, but when you see the popup itself, you learn that it’s part of a long-running email capture strategy.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="611" height="372" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup.png" alt="Kaufmann Popup" class="wp-image-96808" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup.png 611w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup-300x183.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup-380x231.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup-600x365.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup-57x35.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup-82x50.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup-220x134.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Kaufmann-Popup-385x234.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Become a member of our customer club and enter the giveaway to win a 1,000 kr. gift card. We draw a winner every month.</em></p>





<p>Instead of hosting a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">time-limited</a> giveaway campaign, Kaufmann uses the incentive of gift cards to attract new signups and selects a winner among those every month.</p>



<p>Moreover, rather than choose a physical product that may be subject to taste, the company offers you a gift card to make sure that you come back to their store and, thereby, spend above the amount. Even if you don’t win, Kaufmann gets to market to you with relevant offers.</p>



<p>Kaufmann also frames its email popup around a sense of exclusivity by asking you to become a member of its <em>customer club. </em>You may not be a Kaufmann customer at this point yet, but if/when you do sign up, you’ll be one of the <em>insiders.</em></p>



<p>So, even if the chance of winning 1,000 kr. store credit didn’t convince you, Kaufmann can still do that with its <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/persuasive-copywriting-techniques" target="_blank">persuasive copywriting</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Sleeknote Insider Tip</h3>



<p>If you have an <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">email capture popup</a> on your store, make sure to hide it from your existing subscribers. Here’s how you can do that with one click with Sleeknote:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img width="650" height="361" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Newsletter-Subscriber.gif" alt="Newsletter Subscriber" class="wp-image-96840"/></figure></div>
</div></div>





<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Further Reading</strong></h3>





<ul><li><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-popup-best-practices" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">9 Email Popup Best Practices That Will Drive More Conversions</a></li></ul>
</div></div>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Helm’s Product Recommendation Popup</strong></h2>



<p>There’s a widespread misconception among <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">e-commerce marketers</a>: “Popups are only for collecting emails.” Although most fashion shops still run on this old-school belief, modern apparel brands know how to use popups for <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/popup-use-cases" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">more than collecting emails</a>.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.helm.nu/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Helm</a>, a popular bag and suitcase retailer, is a great example of that. When you visit its homepage, the company, first, greets you with a giveaway popup, similar to the examples above.</p>



<p>In addition to that, Helm knows the importance of timely and relevant <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product recommendations</a>. For example, when you visit the page “Gift Ideas for Him<strong>,</strong>” they show you this popup:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="984" height="914" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers.png" alt="Helm Bestsellers" class="wp-image-96800" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers.png 984w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-300x279.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-768x713.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-380x353.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-600x557.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-760x706.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-38x35.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-54x50.png 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-528x490.png 528w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-220x204.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-385x358.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 984px) 100vw, 984px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Our Absolute Bestsellers: For men who want to have quality and functionality at the same time.</em></p>





<p>However, if you’re on the page “Gift Ideas for Her<strong>,</strong>” this is what you see:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="953" height="954" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2.png" alt="Helm Bestsellers 2" class="wp-image-96796" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2.png 953w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-300x300.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-150x150.png 150w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-768x769.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-380x380.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-600x601.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-760x761.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-35x35.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-50x50.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-489x490.png 489w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-220x220.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-385x385.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Bestsellers-2-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 953px) 100vw, 953px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Our Absolute Bestsellers: For women who want to have space for everything in a light and beautiful shoulder bag.</em></p>





<p>The content of both popups is the same: three bestsellers from each category. But the page-specific targeting makes Helm’s product recommendation popups highly unique and personalized.</p>



<p>In both popups, Helm also uses a brilliant <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/copywriting-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">copywriting</a> strategy by describing its ideal buyer: “For men who want to have quality and functionality in one.” If you identify yourself with this definition, it becomes easier to click through the popup.</p>



<p>Helm finds another use case for their popups, this time on its <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product pages</a>. When you’re about to leave certain product pages on the shop, Helm shows you this <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/exit-intent-popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">exit-intent popup</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="723" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-1024x723.png" alt="Helm Popup" class="wp-image-96804" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-1024x723.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-300x212.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-768x542.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-380x268.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-600x424.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-760x536.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-694x490.png 694w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-220x155.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup-385x272.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Helm-Popup.png 1285w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Did you see? We have lots of bags at extra sharp prices. Now you can save more on our beautiful bags on sale.</em></p>





<p>The company knows that one of the reasons why you might be leaving can be the price. That’s why they smartly guide you to their discounted products with this popup.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Sleeknote Insider Tip</h3>



<p>If you want to copy Helm’s brilliant page-specific popup strategy, you can use our Specific URL condition and show your popups only on the pages you specify.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img width="650" height="361" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Specific-URL.gif" alt="Specific URL" class="wp-image-96872"/></figure></div>
</div></div>





<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Further Reading</strong></h3>





