</div></div>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Miinto’s Sales Promotion Popup</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re running a fashion store, you’re likely experimenting with different <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/sales-promotion-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">sales promotion</a> campaigns, be it clearance sales, seasonal offers, or daily deals.</p>



<p>If so, you also know that email is one of the best channels to promote your sales campaigns. For that to work, you need an email list with subscribers interested in your upcoming sales. Luckily, there’s a smart way of making that happen and <a href="http://miinto.dk" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Miinto</a>, the fashion store, knows this well.</p>



<p>Following popup best practices, when you visit its website, Miinto shows you a subtle bottom-right teaser, first:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="529" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-1024x529.png" alt="Miinto Teaser" class="wp-image-96828" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-1024x529.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-300x155.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-768x397.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-1536x794.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-2048x1059.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-380x196.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-600x310.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-760x393.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-1440x745.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-97x50.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-740x383.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Teaser-385x199.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Once you see the teaser that reads “Get VIP Discount Code” and scroll down the page, this popup shows:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="736" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-1024x736.png" alt="Miinto Early Access Popup" class="wp-image-96820" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-1024x736.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-300x216.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-768x552.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-380x273.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-600x431.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-760x546.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-682x490.png 682w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-220x158.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-385x277.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup.png 1334w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Get a VIP Discount Code when we hold our Summer Sale: Sign up for our newsletter and receive our Summer Sale VIP code before anyone else. The code will be sent on Monday, May 25th.</em></p>





<p>In it, Miinto offers you the chance to get a VIP discount code for their upcoming summer sale <em>before anyone else. </em>(In exchange for your email address and phone number, of course.)</p>



<p>With this popup, Miinto aims to capture your email address with the exclusivity of its offer, while promoting its summer sale at the same time.</p>



<p>What I particularly like about this early access popup is how Miinto openly writes the date they’ll send your discount code. They set the expectations right from the offset so you know when to revisit the site to grab this deal.</p>



<p>When you sign up through this popup, Miinto asks about your gender in the next step.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="531" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-1024x531.png" alt="Miinto Early Access Popup 2" class="wp-image-96816" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-1024x531.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-300x156.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-768x398.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-380x197.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-600x311.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-760x394.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-1440x747.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-740x384.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2-385x200.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Early-Access-Popup-2.png 1506w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>One last thing… Select your gender. This way we can send you more relevant offers and inspiration.</em></p>





<p>By using a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/multistep" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">multistep popup</a>, Miinto easily segments its new signups and sends them only relevant offers.</p>



<p>When it’s time for their summer sale, they can show a simple popup with the discount code on it, just as they did earlier for their 10th birthday:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="808" height="546" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup.png" alt="Miinto Sale Popup" class="wp-image-96824" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup.png 808w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-300x203.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-768x519.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-380x257.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-600x405.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-760x514.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-52x35.png 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-74x50.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-725x490.png 725w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-220x149.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Miinto-Sale-Popup-385x260.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 808px) 100vw, 808px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Today we’re celebrating our 10th birthday. Only for today, get an extra 10 percent discount on everything.</em></p>





<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Sleeknote Insider Tip</h3>



<p>If you want to follow this strategy and show a discount code only to your newsletter subscribers, use the “Newsletter Subscriber” targeting option from Strategy #2. However, this time, set your popup to show to visitors who&nbsp;<em>already</em>&nbsp;subscribed to your email list.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img width="700" height="390" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Newsletter-Subscriber-2.gif" alt="Newsletter Subscriber 2" class="wp-image-96836"/></figure></div>
</div></div>





<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
