</div></div>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Rosemunde’s Navigation Popup</strong></h2>



<p>Not every popup is meant for sales or conversions.</p>



<p>When used right, popups can act as shopping assistants, helping visitors find their way around your store. This means a better shopping experience for your visitors and a lower bounce rate for your site.</p>



<p><a href="https://rosemunde.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Rosemunde</a>, a Danish fashion e-tailer, has a brilliant example of that. When I visited its website with the .com domain, the company showed me this popup:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="558" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-1024x558.png" alt="Rosemunde Popup" class="wp-image-96864" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-1024x558.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-300x163.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-768x418.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-1536x837.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2048x1116.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-380x207.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-600x327.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-760x414.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-1440x784.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-92x50.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-740x403.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-220x120.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-385x210.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>With the help of <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/geo-targeting">geo-targeting</a>, Rosemunde’s popup detected that I was in Denmark. That’s why the popup copy reads “We think you’re from Denmark. We suggest you use our Danish webshop.” And using the two buttons below, I could select my preferred language.</p>



<p>With this simple popup, Rosemunde guides you to the right store. And now, they can just personalize the website based on your language preferences and, naturally, show you popups in that language, too.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="564" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-1024x564.png" alt="Rosemunde Popup 2" class="wp-image-96860" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-1024x564.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-300x165.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-768x423.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-1536x846.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-2048x1127.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-380x209.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-600x330.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-760x418.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-1440x793.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-91x50.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-740x407.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-220x121.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rosemunde-Popup-2-1-385x212.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Geo-targeted popups are a must for fashion stores, especially if you have localized shops, country-based delivery options, or geographical restrictions. They’re also ideal for announcing new store openings or helping customers find the nearest physical shop.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Sleeknote Insider Tip</h3>



<p>With our geo-targeting option, you can easily show or hide your popups from visitors based on the country, region, or city they’re located in.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img width="700" height="389" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Geo-targeting.gif" alt="Geo-targeting" class="wp-image-96792"/></figure></div>
</div></div>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Floyd’s Shopping Assistance Popup</strong></h2>



<p>With customer acquisition costs going through the roof, many e-commerce marketers have begun acknowledging the effectiveness of <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-content-marketing-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">content marketing.</a></p>



<p>Yet, there’s still a major obstacle stopping most e-tailers from creating content, and it’s the misconception that they need to start a blog with long articles or an active YouTube channel with high-production videos.</p>



<p>If you’ve been thinking of creating relevant and useful content for your audience, small guides are the perfect place to start.</p>



<p>Are you selling sports equipment? Write up a quick at-home workout guide. Do you run a kitchenware store? Create easy recipes and cooking guides.</p>



<p>But what if you’re in fashion?</p>



<p>Norwegian apparel store <a href="https://www.floyd.no/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Floyd</a> has the perfect answer to that. The company regularly creates style guides to help you find the right product, and uses popups to promote them on relevant pages.</p>



<p>For example, in December, they give tips on finding the perfect Christmas party dress:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="874" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-1024x874.gif" alt="Floyd Popup" class="wp-image-96784" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-1024x874.gif 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-300x256.gif 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-768x656.gif 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-380x324.gif 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-600x512.gif 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-760x649.gif 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-41x35.gif 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-59x50.gif 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-574x490.gif 574w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-220x188.gif 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-385x329.gif 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Styling Tips: The Perfect Dress for the Christmas Table</em></p>





<p>Throughout other times of the year, they might help you find the right type of neckline that fits you best:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="850" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup.png" alt="Floyd Popup" class="wp-image-96788" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup.png 850w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-760x420.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-740x409.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Floyd-Popup-385x213.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Guide: Choose the Right Neckline</em></p>





<p>The key is to show your assistance popups on the right pages. Make sure to use page-level targeting and help visitors on, say, the jeans category with a small “how to find the right pair of jeans” guide.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Sleeknote Insider Tip</h3>



<p>To make sure you don’t distract visitors from viewing products, add a scroll trigger to your popups and set it to 35 percent. (According to&nbsp;<a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/popup-statistics">our original research</a>, popups that show after a visitor scrolls 35 percent perform the best.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img width="700" height="389" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Scroll-Trigger.gif" alt="Scroll Trigger" class="wp-image-96868"/></figure></div>
</div></div>




