										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Why You Should Never Buy an Email List (And What You Should Do Instead)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/list-building" rel="category tag">List Building</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Buy Email List [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-89740" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-Email-List-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e958a30d0552" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As an e-commerce marketer, you probably understand the potency of </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing"><span style="font-weight: 400;">email marketing</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
</div>






<p>It’s one of the best strategies for reaching a widescale audience and nurturing leads until they’re ready to buy.</p>



<p>And with a median ROI of <a href="https://www.lyfemarketing.com/blog/email-marketing-roi/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">122 percent</a>, it’s usually an excellent digital marketing investment.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Getting the ball rolling, however, takes time, and you may struggle during the initial phases of building an email list.&nbsp;</p>



<p>As a result, it may be tempting to take a short cut and do something to hasten the process, such as buying an email list.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But this is always a bad idea and almost never ends well.&nbsp;</p>



<p>In this post, I’ll explain some precise reasons why you should never buy an email list and offer more effective alternatives while highlighting examples from successful brands.&nbsp;</p>



<p>That way, you’ll know how to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">grow your email list</a> the right way and keep your e-commerce brand on the right track.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6b6231abd15" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">FREE DOWNLOADABLE BONUS</p>
