</div>


<h2>Table of Contents</h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. It’s Illegal</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. It’s Unethical</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. You’ll Likely Experience High Spam Complaints</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. You’ll Have Low Engagement</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. It Creates Friction With Shoppers</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. You Won’t Have Exclusive Contacts</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">7. Your Brand Credibility Will Take a Hit</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. It’s Illegal</strong></h2>



<p>For starters, you should know that buying an email list is actually considered illegal and violates two specific laws/regulations.</p>



<p>First, there’s the CAN-SPAM Act, which states that it’s illegal to email consumers without their permission.&nbsp;</p>



<p>It comes with some harsh penalties that can be extremely costly for your company.</p>



<p>According to the CAN-SPAM Act, “Each separate email in violation of the law is subject to penalties of <a href="https://www.ftc.gov/tips-advice/business-center/guidance/can-spam-act-compliance-guide-business" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">up to $43,280</a>, and more than one person may be held responsible for violations.”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="432" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-1024x432.png" alt="Can Spam Act" class="wp-image-89796" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-1024x432.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-300x126.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-768x324.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-380x160.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-600x253.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-760x320.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-83x35.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-119x50.png 119w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-740x312.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-220x93.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15-385x162.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-15.png 1357w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.ftc.gov/tips-advice/business-center/guidance/can-spam-act-compliance-guide-business"></a></p>



<p>Getting hit with something like this can be a death blow to many brands and isn’t a situation you want to find yourself in.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Second, there’s the General Data Protection Regulation (GDRP), which is a data privacy act that was passed in mid-2018.</p>



<p>It applies to businesses that sell to customers within the European Union as well as the European Economic Area.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Under this regulation, you must have explicit consent before sending emails, which, according to the GDPR, means a person must opt-in manually through a checkbox that isn’t pre-checked on your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-site-search" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">e-commerce site</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>So obviously buying an email list and sending out content without a person’s consent is a big no-no.</p>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. It’s Unethical</strong></h2>



<p>Besides the legal issues, it’s also extremely unethical to buy an email list.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Just put yourself in a recipient’s shoes for a second.</p>



<p>Would you want to have your inbox littered with unsolicited offers from pushy companies you’ve never heard of and never signed up for their newsletter?</p>



<p>Of course not.</p>



<p>I find it a constant battle to purge my inbox of spam and unwanted email, and I’m sure it’s the same for many other people.</p>



<p>So all legalities aside, you don’t want to be an e-commerce brand that’s adding to this problem.&nbsp;</p>



<p>It’s bad digital marketing karma.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Instead, you want to stay ethical and do your best to deliver a great customer experience.&nbsp;</p>



<p>That’s why I often recommend using a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/single-opt-in-vs-double-opt-in" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">double optin</a> where a shopper first signs up for your newsletter and then confirms their subscription before you start sending them anything.</p>



<p>Here’s an example from Horti, a plant subscription service for “people who want to create and care for indoor gardens.”&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="490" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-1024x490.png" alt="Horti Homepage" class="wp-image-89756" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-1024x490.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-1536x735.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-600x287.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-1440x689.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-740x354.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-19.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Shoppers first enter their email address at the bottom of Horti’s website in the optin box.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="490" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-1024x490.png" alt="Lets Be Friends Newsletter" class="wp-image-89752" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-1024x490.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-1536x735.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-600x287.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-1440x689.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-740x354.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-18.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>After doing this, they receive a confirmation email where they can click on, “Yes, I want to subscribe.”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="543" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-1024x543.png" alt="Subscribtion Confirmation" class="wp-image-89772" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-1024x543.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-300x159.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-768x407.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-380x201.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-600x318.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-760x403.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-66x35.png 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-94x50.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-740x392.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-220x117.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21-385x204.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-21.png 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This ensures that anyone who signs up truly wants to, which can eliminate a lot of problems and brings me to my next point.&nbsp;</p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. You’ll Likely Experience High Spam Complaints</strong></h2>



<p>The spam battle has been raging for years.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Fortunately, there’s been a significant drop in the global spam volume over the past decade, but <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/420400/spam-email-traffic-share-annual/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">45.3 percent</a> of all emails were still classified as spam in 2018.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="901" height="535" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20.png" alt="Spam Complaints" class="wp-image-89788" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20.png 901w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-300x178.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-768x456.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-380x226.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-600x356.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-760x451.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-59x35.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-740x439.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-220x131.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-20-385x229.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/420400/spam-email-traffic-share-annual/"></a></p>



<p>That’s still quite a bit.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Buying an email list and sending content to subscribers without their permission means you’re contributing to this problem, and you can bet that a high percentage of recipients will mark your emails as spam as a result.&nbsp;</p>



<p>And this is problematic because your Sender Score will drop with your email service provider, which can result in your account being closed as well as fines.</p>



<p>And in some cases, it can even lead to an email service provider taking legal action against you if there’s been a serious violation.&nbsp;</p>



<p>For instance, <a href="https://www.aweber.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Aweber</a> has a very clearly written Anti-Spam Policy on their site.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="429" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-1024x429.png" alt="Anti-Spam Policy" class="wp-image-89804" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-1024x429.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-300x126.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-768x322.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-380x159.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-600x251.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-760x318.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-84x35.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-119x50.png 119w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-740x310.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-220x92.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17-385x161.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-17.png 1359w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.aweber.com/antispam.htm"></a></p>



<p>They state that users aren’t allowed to “send email to people who have not specifically requested information” or “use email lists they purchased, rented, leased, or in any way bought from a third party.”&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="409" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-1024x409.png" alt="Things You Can Not Do With Aweber" class="wp-image-89760" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-1024x409.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-300x120.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-768x307.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-380x152.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-600x240.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-760x304.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-88x35.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-125x50.png 125w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-740x296.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-220x88.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20-385x154.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-20.png 1359w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.aweber.com/antispam.htm"></a></p>



<p>They also highlight the specific consequences.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="429" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-1024x429.png" alt="What Happens If You Try To Spam" class="wp-image-89792" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-1024x429.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-300x126.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-768x322.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-380x159.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-600x252.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-760x319.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-83x35.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-119x50.png 119w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-740x310.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-220x92.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17-385x161.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-17.png 1357w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.aweber.com/antispam.htm"></a></p>



<p>Termination of the account and receiving no refunds is guaranteed, and there may be charges and/or legal action.&nbsp;</p>



<p>So as you can see, things can get ugly in a hurry if you receive a lot of spam complaints, and buying an email list is a surefire way to exacerbate this issue.&nbsp;</p>



<p>A better approach for quickly building your email list and getting shoppers excited about signing up is to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">offer an incentive like a discount</a>.</p>



<p>Take classic men’s clothing company <a href="https://www.taylorstitch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Taylor Stitch</a> for example.</p>



<p>To get shoppers’ attention, they offer 20 percent off their first purchase.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="428" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-1024x428.png" alt="Taylor Stitch Optin" class="wp-image-89780" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-1024x428.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-300x126.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-768x321.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-380x159.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-600x251.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-760x318.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-84x35.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-120x50.png 120w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-740x310.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-220x92.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17-385x161.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-17.png 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.taylorstitch.com/"></a></p>



<p>This is a great way to capture shoppers’ attention and should have a positive impact on their overall conversion rate.&nbsp;</p>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. You’ll Have Low Engagement</strong></h2>



<p>Whenever you send emails to people who didn’t sign up and don’t have a genuine interest in your brand, low engagement will inevitably follow.</p>



<p>It’s simply unrealistic to expect good email performance when you’re resorting to ultra spammy tactics like buying an email list.&nbsp;</p>



<p>According to recent HubSpot data, the average open rate across 28 industries is <a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/sales/average-email-open-rate-benchmark" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">32 percent</a>. As for the average click-through-rate, it usually hovers somewhere around <a href="https://www.campaignmonitor.com/blog/email-marketing/2019/03/what-is-a-good-email-click-through-rate-for-2019/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">2.5 percent</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But if you’re buying your contacts where you’re essentially using a “spray and pray” technique, these numbers are nearly guaranteed to plummet.&nbsp;</p>



<p>After all, these aren’t qualified contacts who are interested in your brand and want to know more about you.&nbsp;</p>



<p>They’re simply random people who ended up on a list you purchased. So you can’t expect them to engage with you.&nbsp;</p>



<p>One of the best ways to raise engagement, however, is to infuse plenty of personalization into your campaign.</p>



<p>Take this email from online retailer <a href="https://www.crateandbarrel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Crate &amp; Barrel</a>, for example.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="635" height="900" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20.png" alt="Crate And Barrel" class="wp-image-89768" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20.png 635w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20-212x300.png 212w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20-380x539.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20-600x850.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20-35x50.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20-346x490.png 346w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20-220x312.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image7-20-385x546.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px" /></figure></div>



<p>They address the subscriber by name and offer personalized furniture recommendations that are unique to each customer.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Or take this one from women’s clothing company <a href="https://www.google.com/aclk?sa=l&amp;ai=DChcSEwjOxJCsr-znAhVTgbIKHSxmAjgYABACGgJscg&amp;sig=AOD64_2Sy5LB1SlDYncs684eBvRbxEZTXg&amp;q=&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi-v4qsr-znAhWEyKYKHaqjB6wQ0Qx6BAgUEAE&amp;adurl=" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Zalando</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="573" height="617" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19.png" alt="Zalando" class="wp-image-89776" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19.png 573w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19-279x300.png 279w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19-380x409.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19-46x50.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19-455x490.png 455w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19-220x237.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-19-385x415.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px" /></figure></div>



<p>They offer access to exclusive sales and specific <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendation-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">product recommendations</a> based on prior behavior.&nbsp;</p>



<p>That way, shoppers receive content that truly interests them and links to products they’re likely to click on.&nbsp;</p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. It Creates Friction With Shoppers</strong></h2>



<p>The entire purpose of email marketing is to build rapport and trust with subscribers over time. It’s the ultimate way for e-commerce brands to nurture relationships.</p>



<p>When you go about it the right way by building an email list from scratch, you can form positive relationships where a good portion of subscribers ultimately become loyal customers.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But when you go about it the sketchy way by buying a list, you’re instantly creating friction from the start and setting the stage for turmoil.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Just think about it.&nbsp;</p>



<p>If you were an e-commerce shopper, who would you be more receptive to?&nbsp;</p>



<p>A brand with a newsletter that you willingly signed up to with news and offers you’re legitimately interested in?&nbsp;</p>



<p>Or a brand that obtained your email address through unscrupulous methods that you’ve never even heard of?</p>



<p>It’s always the former.</p>



<p>If your goal is to build long-term relationships and a devoted group of brand advocates, buying an email list is certainly not the way to go about it. Doing this sows discord right from the start.</p>



<p>A better approach is to build your own list by being upfront with shoppers about what they’ll get and providing them with real value.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://www.bando.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">ban.do</a>, “a clothing, accessories, stationery, tech and gift brand that encourages joy,” does a great job of this with their optin box.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="434" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-1024x434.png" alt="Bando Homepage" class="wp-image-89764" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-1024x434.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-300x127.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-768x326.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-380x161.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-600x255.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-760x322.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-82x35.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-118x50.png 118w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-740x314.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-220x93.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17-385x163.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-17.png 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.bando.com/"></a></p>



<p>Here they briefly explain the perks of signing up, including getting access to new product releases, inspiration, and 10 percent off.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="421" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-1024x421.png" alt="Brighten Up Your Inbox" class="wp-image-89800" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-1024x421.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-300x123.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-768x316.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-380x156.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-600x247.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-760x313.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-85x35.png 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-122x50.png 122w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-740x304.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-220x91.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17-385x158.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-17.png 1361w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.bando.com/"></a></p>



<p>It’s all about letting shoppers know what’s in it for them by signing up.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Do that, and you should be in good shape.&nbsp;</p>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. You Won’t Have Exclusive Contacts</strong></h2>



<p>Also, keep in mind that you don’t have exclusive rights when you buy an email list.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Companies that sell email addresses are in it to make a profit and obviously aren’t concerned with running an ethical business.</p>



<p>Therefore, they usually sell the same email addresses over and over again, meaning your contacts will often receive a large volume of emails from numerous companies.</p>



<p>As I mentioned earlier, this tends to result in most people marking these messages as spam.</p>



<p>However, when it gets to the point that they’re completely barraged with emails, many people will simply shut down their accounts to stop the issue.&nbsp;</p>



<p>This, of course, is problematic because your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-deliverability" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">deliverability rate</a> will plummet, and the emails you send will never reach most of your prospects anyway.&nbsp;</p>



<p>So to say that the contacts you reach through buying an email list are unqualified is an understatement.&nbsp;</p>



<p>In many cases, your efforts are completely futile because your messages will never reach the majority of the contacts on your list.&nbsp;</p>



<p>That’s why it’s so important 1) to gain subscribers through legitimate means and 2) send easily recognizable emails where shoppers can instantly identify your brand.</p>



<p>Men’s clothing and accessories company <a href="https://bonobos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Bonobos</a> does a great job of this with this email featuring their chino range.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="290" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-19.png" alt="Love The Pants You Are In" class="wp-image-89744" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-19.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-19-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-19-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-19-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-19-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-19-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-19-385x186.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<p>Their name is displayed front and center at the top, and the messaging jives with their fun and playful brand identity.</p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Your Brand Credibility Will Take a Hit</strong></h2>



<p>When you put all of this together, you can pretty much guarantee that buying an email list is going to hurt your brand credibility.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Whether it’s the fact that you’re breaking the law, receiving a high volume of spam complaints, or simply being annoying, it’s not going to do your reputation any favors.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Over time, people will remember your company as one that sends unsolicited emails, which will create the type of negative brand awareness you don’t want.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Word gets around quickly these days through review sites and social media, and you don’t want to have your name associated with shady email practices.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Fortunately, it’s not that hard to build a legitimate list of engaged subscribers who genuinely want your updates.</p>



<p>It all boils down to delivering value and giving them something to get excited about.</p>



<p>I think that houseplant company <a href="https://rooted.nyc/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Rooted</a> NYC is a good example.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="433" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-1024x433.png" alt="Rooted Homepage" class="wp-image-89784" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-1024x433.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-300x127.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-768x325.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-380x161.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-600x254.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-760x321.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-83x35.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-118x50.png 118w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-740x313.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-220x93.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19-385x163.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-19.png 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://rooted.nyc/"></a></p>



<p>They clearly state that subscribers don’t have to worry about spam and that they get inside access to product drops, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/giveaway-ideas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">giveaways</a>, and plant care tips.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="433" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-1024x433.png" alt="Rooted Optin" class="wp-image-89748" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-1024x433.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-300x127.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-768x325.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-380x161.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-600x254.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-760x322.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-83x35.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-118x50.png 118w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-740x313.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-220x93.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21-385x163.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-21.png 1361w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://rooted.nyc/"></a></p>



<p>And they back it up by sending interesting emails like this one that introduces a new line of plants that many shoppers will be curious about.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="599" height="495" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17.png" alt="Faux Plants" class="wp-image-89808" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17.png 599w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17-300x248.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17-380x314.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17-61x50.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17-593x490.png 593w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17-220x182.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-17-385x318.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px" /></figure></div>


