<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Customize Design for Different Devices to Avoid Annoying Google</strong></h2>



<p>A few years ago, Google announced its <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/mobile-friendly-popup" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">new interstitials policy</a>.<br></p>



<p>That scared a lot of marketers because it meant site owners could be punished if intrusive popups were misused on mobile.<br></p>



<p>But that doesn&#8217;t mean you can’t use them, period. It just means you have to know <em>how</em> to design mobile popups to follow best practices.<br></p>



<p>Because you have less screen space on mobile, you need to reduce the number of elements included in your popup.<br></p>



<p>With Sleeknote, you can create a desktop popup and then switch to mobile view and unlink and edit the elements you want to change for mobile.<br></p>



<p>That way, you don’t have to create two separate popups, but only adjust the mobile version of your popup.<br></p>



<p>There are a few things to consider when editing the design of your mobile popup:<br></p>



<ol><li>You should always unlink the elements you want to change so the changes you make in your mobile popups doesn’t affect your desktop version.</li><li>If you have a background image on your desktop popup, you should remove it on mobile (it tends to look confusing with the limited space).</li><li>Don’t use more than two input fields in your mobile popup. If people have to scroll on their mobile screen to see your entire mobile popup, it has too much content (which will show in your conversion rates).</li><li>You should shorten your copy to only include the most essential information.</li><li>You should use smaller fonts to make better use of the limited space.</li></ol>



<p>Let me show you what it looks like in action.<br></p>



<p>Here’s a desktop popup I designed:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="723" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-1024x723.jpg" alt="Sleeknote Desktop Example" class="wp-image-86959" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-1024x723.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-300x212.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-768x542.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-380x268.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-600x424.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-760x536.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-50x35.jpg 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-71x50.jpg 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-694x490.jpg 694w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-220x155.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example-385x272.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sleeknote-Desktop-Example.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And here’s the mobile version adjusted to follow the above best practices:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example.jpg" alt="Mobile SleekBox Example" class="wp-image-86919" width="450" height="757" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example-178x300.jpg 178w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example-380x639.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example-21x35.jpg 21w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example-30x50.jpg 30w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example-291x490.jpg 291w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example-220x370.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mobile-SleekBox-Example-385x647.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px" /></figure></div>



<p>As you can see, the two popups still match in design and the message is the same in both. But the design has been tweaked specifically for the device they’re shown on to account for the change in screen space.<br></p>



<p>I know, there’s a lot to think about. But when done right, mobile popups work.<br></p>





<h2 id="8"><strong>8. Use Color Contrast to Highlight Text and Actions</strong></h2>



<p>Finding the right colors to use in your popups is tough if you’re not a designer (trust me, I know).<br></p>



<p>A good rule of thumb is to avoid using the same color throughout your popup. If you’re keen on one color, use different shades of that color to make your popup look more attractive. You can also use contrasting colors. (This especially applies when you use background images.)<br></p>



<p>When your popups have background images, it can be hard to match the font color to the background without making it look unreadable.<br></p>



<p>So, find a contrast color to the main color in your background image and use that for the elements you want it to stand out.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For example, your headline and your CTA button:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="858" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-1024x858.jpg" alt="Color Contrast SleekBox Example" class="wp-image-86887" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-1024x858.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-300x252.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-768x644.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-380x319.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-600x503.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-760x637.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-42x35.jpg 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-60x50.jpg 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-584x490.jpg 584w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-220x184.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example-385x323.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Color-Contrast-SleekBox-Example.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Using contrast colors will help draw attention to your popup without making it look unattractive.<br></p>





<h2 id="9"><strong>9. Get Your Spacing Right (Without a Graphic Designer)</strong></h2>



<p>Many marketers forget spacing when they create their popups. The spacing is the “invisible” content in your popup. And if the spacing in your popup is off, it will look bad and likely affect your conversion rate.<br></p>



<p>The most important thing when you deal with spacing is <em>consistency</em>. Avoid using different spacing on all four sides of your popup.<br></p>



<p>In fact, it’s best if you always have the same spacing in the top and bottom of your popup:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="551" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-1024x551.jpg" alt="An Example of a SleekBox with Proper Spacing" class="wp-image-86871" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-1024x551.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-300x162.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-768x413.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-380x205.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-600x323.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-760x409.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-65x35.jpg 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-93x50.jpg 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-740x398.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-220x118.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing-385x207.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/An-Example-of-a-SleekBox-with-Proper-Spacing.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Another important spacing rule is adjusting the spacing so you don’t have single words on one line in your popup. If you do, you can drag the spacing out or in so you get one less or one more sentence depending on what looks best:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="854" height="506" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-to-Adjust-Spacing-for-a-SleekBox.gif" alt="How to Adjust Spacing for a SleekBox" class="wp-image-86907"/></figure></div>



<p>When you get your spacing right, your popup will look much more professional and that will show in your conversion rates.<br></p>





<h2 id="10"><strong>10. Create New Shape Illusions with .png Images</strong></h2>



<p>I’ve already mentioned how you can experiment with different shapes in your popups.<br></p>



<p>But there’s another way to make the shape of your popup stand out:<br></p>



<p><em>Using .png images with a transparent background.</em><br></p>



<p>When you set a .png image as the background of your container and set the background color of your popup to transparent, your image will create the illusion of a unique shape.<br></p>



<p>Let me show you an example. This is from <a href="https://www.billeje.info/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Billeje.info</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="563" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-1024x563.jpg" alt="Billeje SleekBox Example" class="wp-image-86879" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-1024x563.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-300x165.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-768x422.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-380x209.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-600x330.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-760x418.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-64x35.jpg 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-91x50.jpg 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-740x407.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-220x121.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-385x212.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The actual popup is rectangular but because the background is transparent, the image defines the shape of the popup.<br></p>



<p>Here it is on the website:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="562" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-1024x562.jpg" alt="Billeje SleekBox Example with a Transparent Form" class="wp-image-86875" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-1024x562.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-300x165.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-768x422.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-380x209.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-600x330.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-760x417.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-64x35.jpg 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-91x50.jpg 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-740x406.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-220x121.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form-385x211.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Example-with-a-Transparent-Form.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And here’s what it would look like if the background of the form was white instead of transparent:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="562" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-1024x562.jpg" alt="Billeje SleekBox Ezample with a White Form" class="wp-image-86883" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-1024x562.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-300x165.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-768x422.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-380x209.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-600x330.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-760x417.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-64x35.jpg 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-91x50.jpg 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-740x406.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-220x121.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form-385x211.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Billeje-SleekBox-Ezample-with-a-White-Form.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Looks much better with the transparent background, right?<br></p>



<p>When your popup stands out on your site and looks creative, your visitors are more likely to notice it and take action.<br></p>





<h2 id="11"><strong>11. How to Choose the Right Fonts for Your Popup</strong></h2>



<p>We can’t talk about design best practices without talking about fonts.<br></p>



<p>If you’re ever in doubt about which fonts to use in your popup, go with the most used font on your website.<br></p>



<p>Being creative with your fonts can pay off if you do it right.<br></p>



<p>When you alternate between different fonts in your popup, there are a few best practices to follow:<br></p>



<ul><li>Use creative fonts for headlines to capture attention.</li><li>Use your standard website font for the copy to increase readability and ensure your message isn’t lost.</li><li>Don’t use more than three different fonts in your popup.</li></ul>



<p>Here’s an example of how you can experiment with different fonts:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="693" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-1024x693.jpg" alt="Creative Fonts Example" class="wp-image-86891" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-1024x693.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-300x203.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-768x520.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-380x257.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-600x406.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-760x514.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-52x35.jpg 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-74x50.jpg 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-724x490.jpg 724w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-220x149.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example-385x261.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Creative-Fonts-Example.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you create your next popup, try using a fun font for your headline and test it against your standard website font.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Just make sure that your copy is always easy to read and understand.</p>


<div id="editors-note-block_5f71d571aa1e9" class="block-editors-note">
