<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>I Took 5 Online Brands and Remade Their Email Popups. Here’s What Happened.</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a>, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/list-building" rel="category tag">List Building</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Popup Makeover [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-113711" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Popup-Makeover-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5fbf74e3a5d4e" class="block-preamble"><p>Today, I’m doing a makeover. But not just any makeover…</p>
</div>






<p>A popup makeover.</p>



<p>#SleeknoteStyle</p>



<p>Here’s the deal:</p>



<ul><li>First, I’ll take five online brands that are using website popups to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">grow their list</a>;</li><li>Then, I’ll address what they could improve;&nbsp;</li><li>Finally, using Sleeknote, I’ll redesign their popups based on how they could perform better.</li></ul>



<p>Let’s get started.</p>


