										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>How to Make a Countdown Timer Popup (+ Examples)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a>, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/list-building" rel="category tag">List Building</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Countdown Timer Popup Example [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-113470" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Popup-Example-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5fbe453473e3f" class="block-preamble"><p><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Limited stocks available. While supplies last. Last chance. </span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">You likely know and use these words in your marketing to create a sense of </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing"><span style="font-weight: 400;">scarcity</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
</div>






<p>When something is about to go away, it becomes more attractive. And to avoid missing out on an otherwise lost opportunity, we take action, often with little afterthought.</p>



<p>While scarcity and urgency are widely used in <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing">email marketing</a>, they’re still underused in website popups. The best way to leverage them on-site is to use <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/countdown-timer">countdown timers</a> in your popups.</p>



<p>After analyzing <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/popup-statistics">1+ billion popups</a>, we found out that popups with a countdown timer convert better than those without a countdown timer <strong>by 112.93 percent.</strong></p>



<p>If you want to learn how to increase your popup conversions by 112.93 percent, too, this post is for you.</p>



<p>First, I’ll share a step-by-step guide to create a countdown popup, and then, introduce six of the best countdown popup use cases that go beyond <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-popups">Black Friday popups</a>.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f406d8dc96" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">FREE DOWNLOADABLE BONUS</p>
