</div>


<h2>Table of Contents</h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. Drive More Email Signups</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Build Excitement for Product Launches</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Tease Your Sales Campaigns</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Promote Limited-Time Offers</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. Reduce Cart Abandonment</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Count Down to Special Days</a></p>



<h2><strong>How to Create a Countdown Popup (Step-by-Step)</strong></h2>



<p>Before we begin…&nbsp;</p>



<p>If you already know how to do this, you can skip this step and <a href="#1">jump directly to countdown timer best practices.</a></p>



<p>And if you’re not using a popup builder that allows you to create a countdown popup with a few clicks, you can <a href="https://sleeknote.com/start-free-trial">start a free Sleeknote trial here</a> and play along.</p>



<p>Let’s jump right in. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f447.png" alt="👇" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>



<p>Once you choose a goal and position for your popup, select a template from our 120+ popup templates:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="650" height="411" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Select-Template.gif" alt="Select Template" class="wp-image-113534"/></figure>



<p>Today, I’ll create an “Autumn Sale” popup. (Hint: Click the link below to use the same template.)</p>


<div id="campaign-template-block_5fbe489173e40" class="block-campaign-template">
    <div class="template-placeholder">
    <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Autumn-Sale-Template.png" title="Create a similar campaign">        <p class="image-caption">Create a similar campaign</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="tag">NEW</div>
        <div class="cta-block-content">
            <p>Like what you see? Load this high-converting template in our editor and customize it to the look and feel of your business.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="https://sleeknote.com/template-signup/?templateId=201805-21-Autumn&#038;goalId=promote">Try it out</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<p>Customize your popup as much or as little as you need. For example, I change the background color to make it match “my” website:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="650" height="411" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Background-Color.gif" alt="Background Color" class="wp-image-113522"/></figure>



<p>Then, I upload my brand’s font and use it in the popup:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="600" height="379" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Change-Font.gif" alt="Change Font" class="wp-image-113526"/></figure>



<p>Once you’re happy with your changes, drag and drop the countdown timer onto your popup and adjust the styling to fit the rest of your design:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="650" height="411" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer.gif" alt="Countdown Timer" class="wp-image-113518"/></figure>



<p>(Hint: Countdown timers work on mobile popups, SleekBars, and teasers, too.)</p>



<p>Next, set an end date for your timer and select its language. (We’ll change the date format based on that.)</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="650" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Settings.gif" alt="Countdown Timer Settings" class="wp-image-113514"/></figure>



<p>Finally, decide what happens when the time runs out. You can show a message that replaces the timer or you can disable the popup completely.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="650" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Countdown-Timer-Disable.gif" alt="Countdown Timer Disable" class="wp-image-113510"/></figure>



<p>Once you set up triggers and targeting options, you’re ready to set your popup live on your site. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f680.png" alt="🚀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>



<p>Now that you know how to create a countdown popup in minutes, let’s talk about how you can use them the right way.</p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>How to Use Countdown Popups</strong></h2>



<p>Contrary to popular belief, there’s more to countdown timers than a simple urgency message.</p>



<p>When used right, countdown popups can help <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies">grow your email list</a>, keep your subscribers engaged, sell more products, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/recipes/how-to-reduce-cart-abandonment">reduce cart abandonment</a>, and more. All without sounding too salesy.</p>



<p>Here are six of the most effective ways to use countdown timers in your popups and why they work so well.</p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Drive More Email Signups</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re already using <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-popup-examples">email popups</a> on your site, you may be asking visitors to join your email list or take part in a competition. But without a deadline to do so, they’ll be less motivated to submit their information.</p>



<p>If you’re running time-bound <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/giveaway-ideas">giveaways</a> among new subscribers, or offering your new signups early access to an event, make it stand out in your popups with a countdown timer, like in this example:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="554" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-1024x554.png" alt="Giveaway_Popup" class="wp-image-113506" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-1024x554.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-300x162.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-768x416.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-380x206.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-600x325.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-760x412.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-65x35.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-92x50.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-740x401.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-220x119.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup-385x208.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Giveaway_Popup.png 1363w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>While it’s a common practice to offer discounts in exchange for email signups, many companies can’t afford discounts for each and every subscriber.</p>



<p>A better way to offer discounts, without hurting profit margins or decreasing your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/perceived-value">perceived value</a>, is to do it for a limited time only. <a href="https://www.wedio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Wedio</a>, a camera rental company, knows this well:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="600" height="377" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Wedio-Multistep.gif" alt="Wedio Multistep" class="wp-image-113502"/></figure>



<p>Instead of having a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-popup-examples">discount popup</a> without an end date, the company uses this incentive sparingly and drives urgency with an attention-grabbing countdown timer in its email popup.</p>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Build Excitement for Product Launches</strong></h2>



<p>Anticipation creates excitement.</p>



<p>Think about the Apple fans sleeping in tents for the newest iPhone model, or how Sony teases PlayStation 5 long before its launch date.</p>



<p>Whether you’re about to launch a new product line, stock hyped products your customers are waiting for, or simply introduce new season items, you can build excitement for your launch with <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/sales-promotion-popup-examples">promotional popups</a>.</p>



<p>Check out this example:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="635" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-1024x635.png" alt="Halloween Popup" class="wp-image-113498" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-1024x635.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-300x186.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-768x476.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-380x236.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-600x372.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-760x471.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-740x459.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-220x136.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup-385x239.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Halloween-Popup.png 1331w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>With a countdown popup like this, you can set expectations for anticipated products and collections.</p>



<p>You can also create a demand for new arrivals by creating mystery or offering a sneak peek. To enhance the feeling of anticipation in your popups, you can count down to the big day.</p>


<div id="campaign-template-block_5fbe497b73e41" class="block-campaign-template">
    <div class="template-placeholder">
    <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Waitlist-Popup.png" title="Create a similar campaign">        <p class="image-caption">Create a similar campaign</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="tag">NEW</div>
        <div class="cta-block-content">
            <p>Like what you see? Load this high-converting template in our editor and customize it to the look and feel of your business.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="https://sleeknote.com/template-signup/?templateId=Black-and-White-Giveaway&#038;goalId=newsletter">Try it out</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<p>It’s a great incentive for visitors to join your email list and for you to get new subscribers who are interested in a product when it launches.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Tease Your Sales Campaigns</strong></h2>



<p>Speaking of counting down to important events, it’s no secret that the promise of an upcoming big sale is a powerful incentive to take action.</p>



<p>Countdown popups of this type work especially well with long-awaited deals, such as clearance sales or <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-strategies">Black Friday</a> offers. You could, for example, create two popups for two visitor groups before your sales begin, and convert each group towards different goals.</p>



<p>You can show subscribers a popup, counting down to the big sale, and ask them to prepare their cart, like this:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="831" height="770" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup.png" alt="Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup" class="wp-image-113490" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup.png 831w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-300x278.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-768x712.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-380x352.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-600x556.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-760x704.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-38x35.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-54x50.png 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-529x490.png 529w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-220x204.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Black-Friday-Sneak-Peek-Popup-385x357.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 831px) 100vw, 831px" /></figure>



<p>For visitors who aren’t already on your list, you can create another popup where you invite them to get early access to the sale:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="822" height="905" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup.png" alt="Early Access Popup" class="wp-image-113486" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup.png 822w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-272x300.png 272w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-768x846.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-380x418.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-600x661.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-760x837.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-32x35.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-45x50.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-445x490.png 445w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-220x242.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Early-Access-Popup-385x424.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 822px) 100vw, 822px" /></figure>



<p>Whether you want to get more people into your email list before your sales campaigns begin or sell more to your existing subscribers when they return to your site, pre-sale popups like the above can help you with both.</p>



<p>Remember to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/advanced-scheduling">schedule your popups</a> in good time before the sale, so you can get the maximum return from them.</p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Promote Limited-Time Offers</strong></h2>



<p>It’s not only big sales you can promote with a countdown timer.</p>



<p>Hourly deals, one-day-only sales, long weekend offers… If you have an offer valid for a limited period, countdown popups can help you promote them the right way by driving urgency.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="689" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-1024x689.png" alt="Flash Sale Popup" class="wp-image-113482" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-1024x689.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-300x202.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-768x517.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-380x256.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-600x404.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-760x512.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-52x35.png 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-74x50.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-728x490.png 728w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-220x148.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup-385x259.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Flash-Sale-Popup.png 1144w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>The key is being subtle, yet grabbing attention at the same time. You want visitors to notice the urgency, but you don’t want to intrude on their shopping experience with an annoying, old-school popup.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Further Reading</strong></h3>



<ul><li><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers">Limited-Time Offers: 10 Creative Ways to Drive More Online Sales</a></li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Reduce Cart Abandonment</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re like most e-commerce marketers, you’re likely going above and beyond to <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-popup-examples">reduce cart abandonment</a> on and off your site.&nbsp;</p>



<p>While doing that, you might be offering (or at least considering) discounts to stop abandoning shoppers. Although discounts are effective in persuading potential customers, incentivizing every abandoning visitor is costly.</p>



<p>My suggestion is to offer discounts or similar benefits in your popups to prevent cart abandonment—but only for a limited time.</p>



<p>Check out this example:</p>


<div id="campaign-template-block_5fbe4a0273e42" class="block-campaign-template">
    <div class="template-placeholder">
    <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Free-Shipping-Popup.png" title="Create a similar campaign">        <p class="image-caption">Create a similar campaign</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="tag">NEW</div>
        <div class="cta-block-content">
            <p>Like what you see? Load this high-converting template in our editor and customize it to the look and feel of your business.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" href="https://sleeknote.com/template-signup/?templateId=AnswerFrequentlyAskedQuestions&#038;goalId=promote">Try it out</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<p>Combine this popup with an <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/exit-intent">exit-intent trigger</a> and you’ll stop abandoning visitors at the right time by highlighting the urgency of your offer.</p>



<p>It’s an effective way to reclaim otherwise lost sales, without encouraging abandoning shoppers or hurting profits all the time.</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Count Down to Special Days</strong></h2>



<p>It’s not only sales campaigns and limited-time deals you can count down to in your popups. Any day that’s an excuse to shop is a day to look forward to.</p>



<p>Whether there’s a special occasion in your niche, such as the National Puppy Day or Earth Day, or a holiday ahead, promote it with a countdown timer in your popups, even if you don’t run a sale.</p>



<p>My personal favorite tactic in fall is to count down to the holidays in December and invite visitors to shop for gifts.</p>



<p>With a popup targeting <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/holiday-gift-guides">gift shoppers</a> and a countdown timer reminding that there’s little time until Christmas, you can drive urgency and nudge visitors to buy gifts from your store, like this:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="615" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-1024x615.png" alt="Christmas Popup" class="wp-image-113474" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-1024x615.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-300x180.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-768x461.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-380x228.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-600x360.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-760x456.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-740x444.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-220x132.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-385x231.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup.png 1213w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>The countdown timer drives urgency and sets expectations for delivery before Christmas. When the time runs out, you can replace this popup with another—this time, targeting last-minute shoppers.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="1024" height="710" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-1024x710.png" alt="Christmas Popup 2" class="wp-image-113458" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-1024x710.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-300x208.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-768x532.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-380x263.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-600x416.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-760x527.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-72x50.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-707x490.png 707w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-220x152.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2-385x267.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Christmas-Popup-2.png 1153w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>Easy, effective, and best of all, possible to set up in advance.</p>


