<h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>



<p>I’ve said it before and I’ll say it again: Popups are the most versatile tools in your marketing arsenal.</p>



<p>When combined with the right persuasion triggers, such as scarcity and urgency, popups can help you achieve different conversion goals.</p>



<p>Now that you know how to create one popup for each of your goals and how to add a countdown timer to your popups with a few clicks of a mouse, it’s your turn.</p>



<p><em>How do you use countdown timers in your popups? Share with us in the comments section.</em><em></em></p>
